The,National,Center,for,Biomedical,Ontology,NCBO,supports,biomedical,researchers,by,providing,online,tools,and,a,web,portal,enabling,them,to,access,review,and,integrate,ontological,resources,The,NCBO,BioPortal,is,an,open,repository,of,biomedical,ontologies,allowing,users,to,search,browse,and,visualize,ontologies,The,National,Center,for,Biomedical,Ontology,BioPortal,API,provides,a,RESTful,interface,for,accessing,the,BioPortal,Supported,services,include,downloads,lists,by,specified,criteria,search,access,to,terms,and,concepts,subtree,extraction,and,much,more,API,responses,may,be,XML,or,JSON,formatted